    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RELATING TO ROUNDING OF CASH PAYMENTS.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Requires the rounding of cash transactions for City taxes, fees, and charges to the nearest 5 cents.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Latest action: CR-96(26)
Reported out for passage on second reading and scheduling of a public hearing.&lt;/p&gt;
